        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Gananda,_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The ambitious plan called for 17,000 homes, 12 community centers, a large shopping mall, and three smaller retail areas.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        14,
        15,
        16,
        17,
        18
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Gananda,_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Green spaces named “Forever Wild” were intended as natural buffers between neighborhoods.",
