        18
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Gananda,_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The city’s flag‑raising ceremony took place on September 20, 1973, marking its official opening.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
