      ],
      "source": "https://kids.kiddle.co/Gananda,_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The first school building, located at 1500 Dayspring Ridge, opened with full utilities and served both students and the community after hours.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
